Text: FW EOL Trading ID Cc Claudia I received a Remedy help desk Ticket stating only that Eric could not get into StackManager on Terminal Server Upon calling him I found out that he actually could get in but only after using his old password He is concerned that his new book is not linked up in StackManager Would you please contact him at your earliest time and assist him with his password and StackManager access Thank you Kevin Hopper Enron Networks LLC Terminal Server Operations Original Message From Saibi Eric Sent Monday October AM To Hopper Kevin Subject FW EOL Trading ID Original Message From Clark Claudia Sent Monday October PM To Saibi Eric Subject EOL Trading ID Citrix Terminal Server ID Corp Log on EnronOnline User ID esaibi Password Hopper Kevin Please contact Claudia Clark x should you have any questions regarding log on
